data.description: This is your opportunity!  Own a charming farmhouse on almost 2 acres while enjoying country life just minutes away from town in this precious 3 bedroom, 3 full bath home! This family home has an oversized primary suite with a brand new en suite bathroom including a clawfoot tub. Secondary rooms are both better than average size plus one has an attached full bath. The country kitchen has open shelving and fantastic views from the kitchen sink to the property. The land has a park like setting with huge trees & large grassy area, a deck with a swimming pool that has all updated equipment plus plenty of room for FFA projects. This home has timeless appeal & design defined by practicality & comfort.
